data.text: @jpoysti @ivigilanteblog @netflix @PrimeVideo Yes, still on Netflix. And at least we're lucky in the US to get typically 13 episodes per season. Some UK shows are basically miniseries. Like 4-8 episodes per season.
@jpoysti @ivigilanteblog I'll definitely finish it. Season 6 is the finale and only has 8 episodes. Just need to focus for a couple more days :)
@ivigilanteblog @jpoysti I'm at about the same point and starting to feel the same way. It's not as deep and twisted as the earlier seasons.
@jpoysti Yeah turns out FU and Spacey were more similar than we imagined way back in season 1.
@jpoysti Claire Underwood is doing a good job though. I just always like FU's sleazy ways much better. :)
@RootofGoodBlog I just watched the first 2 episodes last night. Really enjoyed them. :)
